      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The engine currently runs roughly and requires immediate mechanical attention, and the transmission is showing signs of slipping. Cosmetically, the car has several deep scratches, significant dents, and some rust on the lower panels, while the interior shows heavy wear and staining. This would be an appropriate choice for a dedicated project or for parts salvage.",
