      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in a state of absolute preservation, exhibiting flawless coachwork and a pristine interior that reflects an uncompromising maintenance history. Mechanically, the unit performs to original factory specifications, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade asset that transcends the standard pre-owned market. Inspection will confirm its superlative condition.",
