    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine shape inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been cared for with a ton of love and looks brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
