      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW's naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered by the S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring high-pressure double-VANOS and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example is paired with the tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally perfect, with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and preventative rod bearing replacement already completed. Every mechanical component, from the cooling system to the suspension bushings, remains in factory-fresh condition, ensuring the precise handling and high-revving linear power delivery that defines this M-division icon. Truly a turn-key collector piece for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. No accidents. Garage kept. Full service history. Flawless interior and exterior.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2018 BMW M3 finished in Alpine White over Extended Merino Leather. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and shows zero signs of wear. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with no rock chips, dings, or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the leather bolsters are firm, the carbon fiber trim is flawless, and it still carries that new-car aroma. Mechanically, this M3 is impeccable, featuring a full BMW dealership service history with every interval performed on schedule. It has never seen rain or track time. Equipped with the Competition Package, Executive Package, and brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. All original books, two keys, and a clean title are ready for the next owner. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
